Package client.guiControls.userMain

Class UserLocalDatabase

java.lang.Object
client.guiControls.LocalDatabase
client.guiControls.userMain.UserLocalDatabase
public class UserLocalDatabase
extends ILocalDatabase
Represents a local database for a user. This local database is initiated using data fetched from server. The UserMainController can interact with this database to write or read from it.
